stream toppar.str

read sequence card
!* twenty seven residues
!*
*  FIRST SEQUENCE FOR SECOND IC TEST
*
    27
prl arg gly pro arg gly pro arg gly pro hyp gly pro hyp gly pro hyp gly glu hyp gly glu hyp gly glu hyp gly

GENERATE PROA first none last cter setup warn

IC    PARA ALL  ! fill IC angles and bond values from parameters
PRINT IC
IC  SEED 1 N 1 CA 1 C
IC  BILD
PRINT     COORD

open write unit 2 card name peptide.hyp.prl.pdb
write coor pdb unit 2
close unit 2
stop
